 dipoles and relatively slow\nrelaxation processes in the CT band can be relevant concerning the design of\nDLC based organic PV systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2013 20:00:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2014 18:59:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
