ial time $f(\\text{OPT})$-approximation algorithms for some small\nfunction $f$ (the largest approximation ratio we give is $\\text{OPT}^2$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2013 22:17:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-19"}
