-governed characteristics. The interesting feature of the paper is that the\npumping improves with the thickening behavior for small values of $\\epsilon$ or\nin free pumping ($\\Delta P=0$) and pumping ($\\Delta P>0$) regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2013 11:38:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 May 2018 15:03:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-03"}
